    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_23_12106-12188",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "12106-12188",
      "markText": "她让比利感到不安，纯粹因为她是比利的母亲。她让他感到愧疚，感到自己忘恩负义、软弱无能，因为她千辛万苦给了他生命，让这个生命活在世上，而比利其实根本就不喜欢活在世上。",
      "totalCount": 1750,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=12106&rangeEnd=12188",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=12106&rangeEnd=12188"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_19_946-963",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "946-963",
      "markText": "地底下一定埋着数以吨计的人骨肥料。",
      "totalCount": 1728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=946&rangeEnd=963",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=946&rangeEnd=963"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_21_6740-7015",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "6740-7015",
      "markText": "上帝赐予我 接受我无法改变之事物的平静， 改变可改变之事物的勇气， 以及区分这两者之不同的 永恒智慧。",
      "totalCount": 1656,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=6740&rangeEnd=7015",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=6740&rangeEnd=7015"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_27_19456-19503",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "19456-19503",
      "markText": "上帝赐予我接受我无法改变之事物的平静，改变可改变之事物的勇气，以及区分这两者之不同的永恒智慧。",
      "totalCount": 1530,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=19456&rangeEnd=19503",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=19456&rangeEnd=19503"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_19_11514-11574",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "11514-11574",
      "markText": "我终于明白了，是战争让她如此愤怒。她不想让自己的或任何人家的孩子到战场上去送死。她认为书和电影起的作用是为战争推波助澜。",
      "totalCount": 1430,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=11514&rangeEnd=11574",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=11514&rangeEnd=11574"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_22_6269-6345",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "6269-6345",
      "markText": "门打开时他一阵咳嗽，咳嗽时他拉了稀屎。这一过程符合艾萨克·牛顿爵士的第三运动定律。这一定律告诉我们，每一个作用力都产生一个与其相反方向的同等的反作用力。",
      "totalCount": 1410,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=6269&rangeEnd=6345",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=6269&rangeEnd=6345"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_19_15091-15147",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "15091-15147",
      "markText": "我告诉我的儿子们，任何情况之下他们都不能参与大屠杀，即便是对敌人进行大屠杀的消息，也不应该给他们带来满足和欣喜。",
      "totalCount": 1360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=15091&rangeEnd=15147",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=15091&rangeEnd=15147"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_25_2427-2480",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "2427-2480",
      "markText": "比利以为高力娃与第二次世界大战有关，用微弱的声音把自己的地址告诉他：“施拉赫特霍夫——芬夫”——五号屠场。",
      "totalCount": 1350,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=2427&rangeEnd=2480",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=2427&rangeEnd=2480"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_23_458-520",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "458-520",
      "markText": "特拉法玛多人也不把人类看成双脚直立生物。他们把人看成巨大的千足虫——“一端是婴儿的脚，另一端是老人的脚。”比利·皮尔格林说。",
      "totalCount": 1302,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=458&rangeEnd=520",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=458&rangeEnd=520"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_19_6774-6865",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "6774-6865",
      "markText": "退伍兵决定将电梯厢开到地下室，关了门，开始下降，但他的结婚戒指钩住了门上的铁镶边。于是当电梯厢的地板开始下降，离开他的脚底时，他被悬在了空中，电梯厢顶部砸碎了他的脑壳。事情就是这样。",
      "totalCount": 1242,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=6774&rangeEnd=6865",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=6774&rangeEnd=6865"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_23_7229-7315",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "7229-7315",
      "markText": "只有蜡烛和肥皂是德国产的。两者很相似，都是阴森森的乳白色。英国人无从知道，这些蜡烛和肥皂是用犹太人、吉卜赛人、同性恋者、共产党人以及其他帝国的敌人的尸体熬炼出来的油脂做的。",
      "totalCount": 1170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=7229&rangeEnd=7315",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=7229&rangeEnd=7315"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_19_1283-1337",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "1283-1337",
      "markText": "我祝愿你和你的家人以及你的朋友圣诞快乐新年好，还希望我们如果机会巧了，还能在一个和平自由世界的出租车里相见。",
      "totalCount": 1157,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1283&rangeEnd=1337",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1283&rangeEnd=1337"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021016_23_34533-34555",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "34533-34555",
      "markText": "做这种事她非常兴奋：以爱的名义让他尊严扫地。",
      "totalCount": 1105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021016&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=34533&rangeEnd=34555",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1e332490813ab6eb5g016419?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=34533&rangeEnd=34555"
    },
    {
